OnPage SEO

Search engine optimization (SEO) will help you get noticed. There are many forms of search engine optimization. With the basic package, we review the meta tags that are relevant to your practice and ensure they are tagged and optimized so that you rank higher in search results.

Google-my-page

Local listing of your practice showcases your practice when patients search on Google. All of your local details such as address, phone number, work hours show up prominently on Google. Adding pictures familiarizes your patients with the practice and services.

Directory listing

When patients search for your physicians, it is important that they find the correct information across the web. Oftentimes, the search results bring up a variety of directory listings with wrong or outdated information. We contact these websites and ensure that they all have the most uptodate information on your practice so that patients can reach your practice.
